</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/sup\"><code>String.prototype.sup()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/toLocaleLowerCase\"><code>String.prototype.toLocaleLowerCase()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/toLocaleUpperCase\"><code>String.prototype.toLocaleUpperCase()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/toLowerCase\"><code>String.prototype.toLowerCase()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/toString\"><code>String.prototype.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/toUpperCase\"><code>String.prototype.toUpperCase()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/Trim\"><code>String.prototype.trim()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/trimEnd\"><code>String.prototype.trimEnd()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/trimStart\"><code>String.prototype.trimStart()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/valueOf\"><code>String.prototype.valueOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Vererbung:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/arguments\"><code>Function.prototype.arguments</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/caller\"><code>Function.prototype.caller</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/prototype\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Zusammenfassung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die <strong><code>lastIndexOf()</code></strong> Methode gibt den Index des letzten Vorkommnisses des angegebenen Wertes innerhalb des aufrufenden <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>Strings</code></a> Objekts zurück, oder -1, wenn der Wert nicht gefunden wurde. Der aufrufende String wird rückwärts durchsucht, beginnend beim <code>fromIndex</code>.&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>str</var>.lastIndexOf(<var>searchValue</var>[, <var>fromIndex</var>])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"searchvalue\"><code>searchValue</code></dt>\n <dd>Ein String mit dem Wert, nach dem gesucht werden soll.</dd>\n <dt id=\"fromindex\"><code>fromIndex</code></dt>\n <dd>Optional. Die Position im aufrufenden String, ab der gesucht rückwärts werden soll. The Position wird gezählt von links nach rechts. Gesucht wird von dieser Position ab nach links. Diese kann jeden Integerwert annehmen. Der Standartwert ist <code>str.length</code>. Wenn der Wert negativ ist, wird 0 verwendet. Wenn <code>fromIndex &gt; str.length</code>, wird <code>str.length&nbsp;</code>statt <code>fromIndex</code> benutzt.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Zeichen in einem String werden von links nach rechts gezählt. Der Index des ersten Zeichens ist 0, der Index des letzten Zeichens ist <code>stringName.length - 1</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token string\">'canal'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lastIndexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// returns 3</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'canal'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lastIndexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// returns 1</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'canal'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lastIndexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// returns -1</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'canal'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lastIndexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'x'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// returns -1</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"case-sensitivity","title":"Groß- und Kleinschreibung","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Die <code>lastIndexOf() </code>Methode unterscheidet zwischen&nbsp;Groß- und Kleinschreibung. Der folgende Ausdruck gibt zum Beispiel <code>-1</code> zurück.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token string\">'Blue Whale, Killer Whale'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lastIndexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'blue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// returns -1</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_using_indexof_and_lastindexof","title":"Beispiel: Benutzung von&nbsp;<code>indexOf()</code> und&nbsp;<code>lastIndexOf()</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Das folgende Beispiel verwendet <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/indexOf\"><code>indexOf()</code></a> und&nbsp;<code>lastIndexOf(),</code> um Werte im String&nbsp;<code>\"Brave new world\" zu finden</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> anyString <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Brave new world'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The index of the first w from the beginning is '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> anyString<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">indexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'w'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Displays 8</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The index of the first w from the end is '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> anyString<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lastIndexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'w'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Displays 10</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The index of \"new\" from the beginning is '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> anyString<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">indexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'new'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Displays 6</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The index of \"new\" from the end is '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> anyString<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">lastIndexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'new'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Displays 6</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Beispiel: Benutzung von indexOf() und lastIndexOf()"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>ECMAScript 1st Edition.</td>\n   <td>Standard</td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.5.4.8\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'String.prototype.lastIndexOf' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-string.prototype.lastindexof\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'String.prototype.lastIndexOf' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompatibilität","title":"Browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Links","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/charAt\"><code>String.prototype.charAt()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/indexOf\"><code>String.prototype.indexOf()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/split\"><code>String.prototype.split()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/indexOf\"><code>Array.prototype.indexOf()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/lastIndexOf\"><code>Array.prototype.lastIndexOf()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Zusammenfassung","id":"summary"},{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"description"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"examples"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Links","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Die lastIndexOf() Methode gibt den Index des letzten Vorkommnisses des angegebenen Wertes innerhalb des aufrufenden Strings Objekts zurück, oder -1, wenn der Wert nicht gefunden wurde. Der aufrufende String wird rückwärts durchsucht, beginnend beim fromIndex.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"String.prototype.lastIndexOf()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"String.prototype.lastIndexOf()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"String.prototype.lastIndexOf()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"String.prototype.lastIndexOf()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"String.prototype.lastIndexOf()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"String.prototype.lastIndexOf()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"String.prototype.lastIndexOf()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"String.prototype.lastIndexOf()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/lastindexof","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/lastindexof/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript-Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Globale Objekte"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String","title":"String"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/lastIndexOf","title":"String.prototype.lastIndexOf()"}],"